I think these are pretty hard to read because of the spacing. I asked ChatGPT for help and we came up with this:
func trimString(s string) string {
	lines := strings.Split(s, "\n")
	for i, line := range lines {
		lines[i] = strings.TrimLeft(line, " \t")
	}
	return strings.Join(lines, "\n")
}
I think we should use it and add tabs/spaes on the left hand side for indending.
